-- MBIA CIO says municipal debt historically cheap
-- 
-- Thu Jan 31, 2008 1:05pm EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/01/31/us-mbia-munis-idUSWEN370020080131

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - MBIA Inc, the world's largest bond insurer, believes municipal debt is cheap by historical standards, and represents a good investment opportunity, Chief Investment Officer Clifford Corso said. 

 Corso spoke on a conference call. (Reporting by Jonathan Stempel; Editing by  Tim Dobbyn )